Dating problems Do you have a crush, boyfriend, or a girlfriend? Maybe you have two and just can't learn to manage them? Post here!
If you have any dating problems that you think other teens might be experiencing and want some insight, advice or commentary from other teens, post here.
If you don't have a girlfriend/boyfriend, please feel free to post about anything you might want to know about, or want advice about?
